title: Machine Learning Workshop for CodeathonX
description: This is a pre-hackathon workshop leading to CodeathonX Kuala Lumpur over April 13-14.
body:
This is a pre-hackathon workshop leading to CodeathonX Kuala Lumpur over April 13-14. We are glad to have Mundher Al-Shabi, Lead AI Engineer at Aerodyne, to speak at this workshop.
